snippet.title: About an Elf – Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Set out in an elf-tastic adventure to strange new lands in search for the fabled elftopia, as Princess Dam and her feline apprentice, Roland the BraveCat, fight for friendship and belonging in a world enslaved by the King of Terrors and his army of evil monsters! Available now on the Nintendo eShop for the Nintendo Switch.
